original_title: The 1995 Mariners: Saving Baseball In Seattle
overview: Chronicling the Mariners' memorable run to their first-ever AL West title in 1995, when a team led by Ken Griffey Jr. and Randy Johnson helped keep baseball in the Pacific Northwest and punctuated the season with a stirring ALDS win over the Yankees.
title: The 1995 Mariners: Saving Baseball In Seattle
